WEBVTT

00:00.297 --> 00:01.851
I have a brother.

00:01.882 --> 00:03.698
It's like your dad cloned himself.

00:03.733 --> 00:05.812
He's been in and out of prison,

00:05.837 --> 00:08.370
basically, for years
until a few months ago.

00:09.839 --> 00:11.940
It wasn't you that was
supposed to be here.

00:11.975 --> 00:13.367
How does it feel?

00:13.392 --> 00:15.328
How does it feel not to be in control?

00:15.353 --> 00:19.623
I've been in love
with Briana, my sister,

00:19.648 --> 00:21.398
for as long as I can remember.

00:21.423 --> 00:22.422
Brady!

00:22.447 --> 00:24.681
I'm not you, okay? I'm not.

00:24.706 --> 00:26.439
I'm not sick like you.

00:26.464 --> 00:28.398
You mean, sick like me, is that it?

00:28.423 --> 00:30.123
You brought this on yourself!

