01:50.020 --> 01:52.287
You gotta call 911.

02:11.874 --> 02:13.326
It's over.

02:15.077 --> 02:17.388
We know who killed Jesse.

02:19.881 --> 02:22.007
You can talk to me now.

02:23.674 --> 02:26.074
You don't understand me.

02:27.923 --> 02:30.290
I tried a different way with you.

02:30.968 --> 02:32.125
To what?

02:32.160 --> 02:33.992
To end the cycle.

02:34.028 --> 02:35.527
This is car 16.

02:35.562 --> 02:38.373
We're closing in on
Brady's phone GPS location.

